titles.title: CB 23 His Name, His Name Shall Be Called Wonderful

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
HIS NAME, HIS NAME SHALL BE CALLED
WONDERFUL.
His name, His name shall be called Counselor.
The Mighty God, the Everlasting Father, the
Prince of Peace through all eternity; the mighty
God, the Everlasting Father, the Prince of Peace
through all eternity.
